# Optional: enables the "Connect Google Drive" import flow.
# Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application) in Google Cloud Console,
# add your dev/prod origins under "Authorized JavaScript origins", and
# enable the Google Drive API for the project. This ID is public (it's sent
# to the browser) — no client secret is needed since SimpleSet uses Google
# Identity Services' client-side token flow.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
